18. How do you manage version control and deployment (Solutions & ALM)?

EXPLAIN IN ANSWER:-
â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”
âœ… I follow ALM (Application Lifecycle Management) best practices using Solutions in Power Apps:

ğŸ‘‰ I use Solutions in Power Apps to group related components like apps, flows, tables, and security roles into a single package together.
ğŸ‘‰ During development, I use Unmanaged Solutions â€” these allow easy editing and collaboration.
ğŸ‘‰ Once the app is tested and finalized, I export it as a Managed Solution for the Production environment.
    which are read-only to ensure stability and controlled updates.
ğŸ‘‰ I also maintain separate environments for Dev, Test, and Prod.
ğŸ‘‰ We move solutions across environments using Export/Import to maintain version control and ensure smooth deployment.
